<br>
&quot;But what about the people who can't afford to go to college?  What about THEM?&quot;<br>
<br>
F#@% THEM!!<br>
<br>
Nobody is given a certificate upon being born that grants them the right to a higher education.  True, not going to college will severely limit your career options, but it won't kill anyone.  We, as a society, need to get it into our heads that some people just CAN'T AFFORD THINGS.  And THAT'S OKAY!!<br>
<br>
Everyone is so caught up in making the playing field even.  People want to make sure everything is fair.  HEAR ME NOW - IT'S NEVER GONNA BE FAIR!<br>
<br>
My parents were in a high income tax bracket, but didn't help me out with my college costs at all.  I worked two jobs and went to school full time, took out a bunch of loans, but finally had to drop out because I couldn't make enough money.<br>
<br>
What really pissed me off was the hundreds of kids that were in low income tax brackets and were going to school for NEARLY FREE while I kicked my own ass trying to make it through.  I couldn't make the money to finish school, so I didn't.  These bastards didn't work a day for 4 years and still graduated mostly debt free!!  Why?  Because I WAS PUTTING IN ENOUGH MONEY FOR 3 EDUCATIONS AND GETTING ONLY ONE!!<br>
<br>
Okay /language_filter OFF.<br>
<br>
FUCK the financial aid system<br>
FUCK the communist Democrat cocksuckers that INVENTED this brilliant system<br>
FUCK low income families who think that they have a God-given right to be anything more than a low income family<br>
FUCK everyone I may have missed. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.bjmay.com/images/Sinead_sig.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
